    <section id="Isis+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Isis Project Incubation Status</title>

      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
      project status, look on the project website.</p>
      <p><span class="graduated">The Isis project graduated on 2012-10-17</span></p>
    </section>

    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>

      <p>The Isis project will be an extensible standards-based framework to
      rapidly develop and enterprise level deploy domain-driven (DDD)
      applications.</p>
    </section>

